            <!-- MODULE 2 -->
            <article class="module--box-shadow-gradient-bg-green-moderate u-span-2" id="technical-skills">
                <span class="module__eyebrow">Technical Skills</span>
                <header class="module__title">
                    <h2 class="module__heading">
                        How This Site Is Built
                    </h2>
                    <p class="module__subheading">
                        A modern, performance-first web stack designed for scalability, SEO, and maintainability. </p>
                </header>
                <section class="card">
                    <header>
                        <h3 class="card__heading">
                            Architecture
                        </h3>
                        <p class="card__subheading">
                            Server-Rendered, Modular by Design
                        </p>
                    </header>
                    <p class="card__body">
                        Pages are rendered on the server to ensure fast initial load times, predictable performance, and
                        full crawlability by search engines. This approach prioritizes real-world performance metrics
                        and avoids unnecessary client-side complexity.
                    </p>
                </section>
                <section class="card">
                    <header>
                        <h3 class="card__heading">
                            Rendering
                        </h3>
                        <p class="card__subheading">
                            Server-Side Rendering for Speed and SEO
                        </p>
                    </header>
                    <p class="card__body">
                        Pages are rendered on the server to ensure fast initial load times, predictable performance, and
                        full crawlability by search engines. This approach prioritizes real-world performance metrics
                        and avoids unnecessary client-side complexity.
                    </p>
                </section>
                <section class="card">
                    <header>
                        <h3 class="card__heading">
                            Styling & Maintainability
                        </h3>
                        <p class="card__subheading">
                            Scalable CSS with Design Systems in Mind
                        </p>
                    </header>
                    <p class="card__body">
                        Styles are written in semantic, BEM-structured CSS with global design tokens defined via CSS
                        variables. This makes the layout responsive across devices while keeping the system easy to
                        extend without refactoring.
                    </p>
                </section>
                <section class="card">
                    <header>
                        <h3 class="card__heading">
                            SEO & Accessibility
                        </h3>
                        <p class="card__subheading">
                            Built for Discoverability and Usability
                        </p>
                    </header>
                    <p class="card__body">
                        Semantic HTML, structured heading hierarchy, accessible navigation patterns, and
                        performance-friendly assets ensure the site is optimized for both search engines and real
                        users—without sacrificing design quality.
                    </p>
                </section>
