                        Clear experimentation roadmaps, statistically valid A/B tests, and sustained lifts in conversion
                        rate, engagement, and downstream revenue
                    </p>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <h3 class="module__title">
                        Global sites that don’t scale cleanly
                    </h3>
                    <p class="solution-icon">
                        Standardized templates, governance models, and workflows supporting consistent execution across
                        regions, languages, and brands
                    </p>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <h3 class="module__title">
                        Unstructured or low-impact experimentation
                    </h3>
                    <p class="solution-icon">
                        Prioritized test backlogs, defined success metrics (CVR, CTR, feature adoption), and documented
                        learnings shared with stakeholders
                    </p>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <h3 class="module__title">
                        Slow or fragmented web workflows
                    </h3>
                    <p class="solution-icon">
                        Streamlined CMS and project management processes that reduce time-to-launch, improve QA
                        accuracy, and increase iteration velocity
                    </p>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <h3 class="module__title">
                        Strategy disconnected from execution
                    </h3>
                    <p class="solution-icon">
                        Web initiatives tied to clear KPIs, launch plans, and post-launch measurement frameworks that
                        inform ongoing optimization
                    </p>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <h3 class="module__title">
                        Cross-functional friction slowing delivery
                    </h3>
